uh, Captain McDonald.

133
00:18:10,823 --> 00:18:14,281
- That was a big misunderstanding.
- Right.

134
00:18:14,426 --> 00:18:17,793
Broke his damn jaw
is what I heard.

135
00:18:17,896 --> 00:18:21,730
