a big "hello."

136
00:18:21,834 --> 00:18:23,961
Whoa. Wait a minute.

137
00:18:24,103 --> 00:18:26,401
Johnson says
I was reinstated.

138
00:18:26,505 --> 00:18:29,133
With the company.
Not with the union.

139
00:18:29,241 --> 00:18:31,971
You owe some dues here,
boy.

140
00:18:32,077 --> 00:18:35,604
- 217 bucks.
- I'll pay that off on this cruise.

141
00:18:35,747 --> 00:18:39,308
No. Nobody ships out if they're
in arrears, you know that.

142
00:18:39,451 --> 00:18:44,252
- How am I gonna pay my dues
if I can't get the job?
- I don't make the rules, mate.

143
00:18:46,058 --> 00:18:49,824
Look, your ride doesn't sail
'til the end of the week.

144
00:18:49,928 --> 00:18:52,488
If I can get the money,
then what?

145
00:18:52,631 --> 00:18:54,792
Then I'll let you
ship out.

146
00:18:56,635 --> 00:18:59,001
I'll get the money.

147
00:19:09,781 --> 00:19:12,511
Keep goin'.
Take it back. Yeah.

148
00:19:12,618 --> 00:19:15,246
Bring it, bring it,
bring it, bring it.

149
00:19:15,387 --> 00:19:17,287
Okay, down.

150
00:19:38,510 --> 00:19:42,378
