Hello, Randal.
I didn't know you had company.

203
00:24:17,656 --> 00:24:20,454
We were just leaving.

204
00:24:23,428 --> 00:24:28,263
- You know, we should go back up there.
- Not now. Not together.

205
00:24:28,366 --> 00:24:31,301
Poe knows something
about my father, obviously.

206
00:24:31,403 --> 00:24:34,167
If you don't want to go back
up there, I'll go myself.

207
00:24:34,272 --> 00:24:37,867
If you want to find your daddy,
you're gonna have to work smarter,

208
00:24:38,009 --> 00:24:40,477
not harder.

209
00:24:40,612 --> 00:24:42,512
Yeah.

210
00:24:47,452 --> 00:24:49,750
- Natasha Binder?
- What's the problem?

211
00:24:49,855 --> 00:24:52,415
I'm afraid I have
some bad news.

212
00:24:52,557 --> 00:24:54,491
They found
your father's body.

213
00:25:20,652 --> 00:25:22,552
I'm sorry.

214
00:25:22,654 --> 00:25:26,454
