your father's body in one of the rooms.

217
00:25:34,766 --> 00:25:37,166
I need to see him.

218
00:25:37,269 --> 00:25:41,171
Your daddy was burned
pretty badly.

219
00:25:42,807 --> 00:25:45,571
The identification had to
be made from dental charts...

220
00:25:45,677 --> 00:25:48,373
